<http://nkust.edu.tw/mislab/cnc/ontology/sth#STHExtendedOntology> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                                                   rdfs:comment "Ontology for CNC smart tool holder monitoring with NC files, NC blocks, sensing windows, multi-sensor alignment, diagnosis, prediction, and communication mapping."@en ;
                                                                   rdfs:label "Extended Smart Tool Holder Ontology with NC File and Sensing Windows"@en .

